So indeed, our line could have been parallel to the plane, or maybe even contained in the plane.

00:21:38.460 --> 00:21:45.480
Well, if a line is parallel to the plane, then maybe what happens is that when we plug in the positions of a moving point,

00:21:46.380 --> 00:21:48.620
we actually get something that never equals 7.

00:21:48.920 --> 00:21:50.320
Because maybe we get actually a constant.

00:21:50.620 --> 00:21:54.360
Say that we have gotten, I don't know, 13 all the time.

